Clear Your Einstein Copilot Feed History

This change applies to Lightning Experience, the Salesforce mobile app for iOS and Android, the Field Service mobile app for iOS and Android, and Sales Cloud Everywhere in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions with the Einstein for Sales, Einstein for Service, or Einstein Platform add-on. Setup for Einstein Copilot is available on the desktop site.

Use the clear history icon to clear your feed and start a new session.

On iOS and Android devices, the feature is available the week of July 1, 2024.
title: Clearing Einstein Copilot Feed History
